channel.title: My Second model: BladeShield
channel.description:
Heya well I was looking through my RSMV and i found a model of a new (Obby?) Shield and an obby knife attached to it.
Well i removed the obby knife, duplicated the shield did some rotating and recoloring and viola. The bladeshield was born.
Well i dont have the Datmaker1.3 because the "naked lady" doesn't work for me so if someone could send me a link to it on a different site? PM would be fine.
If someone could convert it on datmaker so it isnt see through that'd be great.
Picture: [IMG]http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii19/lOIkEoMGiTSmERzA/Bladeshield.png[/img]
Download: (Rar file with Model and Drop Model .MQO) Total File Size: 7.94kb
Mediafire Link: [URL=http://"http://www.mediafire.com/?dfyjzztzh4q"]Here[/URL]
If you use just credit me and Rep is Appreciated ^^
